<h3>Installation process:</h3>
1. Install <a href="https://www.vagrantup.com/docs/installation/">vagrant.
2. Download <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/unnamed01/elevator/master/deploy/Vagrantfile">Vagrantfile</a> and <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/unnamed01/elevator/master/deploy/bootstrap.sh">bootstrap.sh</a> into a directory on your local pc.
3. Being inside that directory type "vagrant up"
4. Open your "/etc/hosts" file, add record "127.0.0.1 elevator.com". For Windows this file is located at C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\hosts
5. In browser open http://elevator.com:4568/emulator/